title: Brady Quinn on Josh Gordon Trade, Week 2 & Seahawks-Bears recap (Football 09/19)
description:
Will Brinson is joined by Sean Wagner to break down the Seahawks-Bears game from Monday night and debate whether Mitchell Trubisky is good and if the Bears defense can propel them to a playoff run. Then, Brady Quinn joins Will to discuss the biggest topics from Week 2 of the NFL season, including the Josh Gordon trade, the Steelers struggles on defense, Patrick Mahomes exploding and much, much more.
